The main directory for Accented ASR experiments. A detailed description of all the files in local repository is given.

ind_run.sh ===> The frontend training script for standalone ASR network(transformer).
dann_train.sh ===> The frontend training script for DAT+ network.
dann_test.sh ===> The frontend inference script for DAT+ network.
train_classifier.sh ===> The frontend training script for standalone pre-training of Accent Classifier.
test_classifier.sh ===> The frontend training script for standalone inference of Accent Classifier.
